CatDescriptText: "Four Roses" advertisement reads "Wouldn't Your Rather Drink Four Roses?"  "Standback Headache Powder" ad hangs from ceiling, neon along the top of the bar with initials "P.T." Jukebox and sign advertising "Thanksgiving Day Football Game?"
TitMainTitle: Interior view of bar, mounted moose head above bar, tin ceiling, striped awning with four roses advertisements, with "Fort Pitt Beer" clock and sign for "Paul Jones"
